PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of W.A. Patrick Reid, of Vancouver, British Columbia, as a part-time director of the Board of Directors of the Canada Ports Corporation and as chairman of the board of directors of the Vancouver Port orporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective December 21, 1990, in the place of Hector Duncan Perry.
